{"tid":94414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫學/宗教jj入]有冇人解釋下Deja Vu","createTime":"2017-01-25T08:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T06:59:23.000Z","uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b382da089672e433a80706ac25ce40c1bd53436","tid":94414,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"好辛苦好辛苦<br />\n程度嚴重到影響生活同情緒<br />\n我成日好驚又出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由幼稚園開始一直有deja vu嘅情況<br />\n電影trailer，日常片段，好多野都可以deja vu<br />\n曾經中學有段時間持續困擾過我一年有多 <br />\n日日夜夜出現 <br />\n幾確定自己係夢入面見過某啲野 但係冇人信<br />\n每次依種感覺出現就會想嘔同暈、頭痛<br />\n之後少左但係keep住過一排就會有<br />\n<br />\n近排又發作<br />\n種感覺係無時無刻都可以出現<br />\n近幾次直情係係夢入面deja vu作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起身差啲嘔出黎<br />\n好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有冇解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a433de5120fde91d1d4abd9263eadb1b55c475d7","tid":94414,"uid":71539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"I've just been in this place before! <br />\n(Higher on the street!) <br />\nAnd I know it's my time to come home!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97ac054b473eac8abb5a1a121c39d625102105","tid":94414,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I've just been in this place before! <br />\n(Higher on the street!) <br />\nAnd I know it's my time to come home!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真你又俾粒膠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31339570e262e66483a860e039e32ff27edae907","tid":94414,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"<block